{"tid":2444501,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"維尼帝: 又話拜登上台會放生我哋？依家華為中興及3間中企 遭美列為危害國安","createTime":"2021-03-12T23:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T00:33:33.000Z","uid":108201,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8664d0bccfd2b818ac99d08d1e58855cb13f4c","tid":2444501,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T23:39:37.000Z","msg":"美國聯邦通訊委員會(FCC)公布，根據2019年通過的法例，把5間中國企業納入危害美國國家安全的名單內。<br />\n<br />\n被列入制裁名單的5間中國企業，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">包括華為、中興電訊(00763)、海能達(Hytera)、海康威視及浙江大華技術。</span></span></strong>FCC去年已經把華為與中興通訊，定性為危害美國國安。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會在2019年通過《安全及可信賴通訊網絡法》(Secure and Trusted Communications Networks Act)，要求FCC確定哪些通訊設備供應商可能危及國家安全。<br />\n<br />\nFCC署理主席Jessica Rosenworcel表示，針對5間中國企業採取行動，目的是確保美國新一代通訊網絡安全。"},{"pid":"de14af7f52f06bb3bb18f9c9bcec925684c38638","tid":2444501,"uid":108201,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T23:39:52.000Z","msg":"下星期中芯國際 小米一齊仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56eff1e59f30bdf235a4c1c78934e09f0e5de35","tid":2444501,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T23:52:35.000Z","msg":"華為可以回家養豬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06b22a77116c203abecbb9a5a18bec6b7d0935e","tid":2444501,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T23:54:25.000Z","msg":"連登仔：at,na,sg,dw,ngth"},{"pid":"c601d74a0bc031efe4fdf2bdca2e4672574388bc","tid":2444501,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d06b22a77116c203abecbb9a5a18bec6b7d0935e","tid":2444501,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T23:54:25.000Z","msg":"連登仔：at,na,sg,dw,ngth"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T23:58:54.000Z","msg":"All in TSM AMAT and NXPI <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b180dfe53eee32d609139aa3fb55217be27d7aca","tid":2